               stealing a cloth coat, value 4 s. a cloth waistcoat, value 2 s. a pair of leather breeches, value 10 s. a pair of cotton stockings, value 6 d. a pair of thread stockings, value 6 d. two linen shirts, value 2 s. two linen stocks, value 6 d. two guineas, and a half guinea, the property of 
                     
